# Writerly File Path Testing

This document contains various file path examples to test the "Open File Under Cursor" functionality.

## Existing Files (These should work)

### Relative Paths
- Package info: ../package.json
- README: ../README.md
- License: ../LICENSE
- TypeScript config: ../tsconfig.json
- Logo PNG: ../logo.png
- Logo SVG: ../logo.svg

### Quoted Paths
- "Package JSON": "../package.json"
- 'License file': '../LICENSE'
- `Config file`: `../writerly.configuration.json`

### Mixed Content Examples
Check the configuration in ../package.json for extension details.
The main logo is stored at "../logo.png" and SVG version at '../logo.svg'.
You can find the license terms in `../LICENSE` file.

## Different File Types

### Images (should open in image viewer)
- PNG image: ../logo.png
- SVG vector: ../logo.svg

### Documents (should open in text editor/viewer)
- Markdown: ../README.md
- JSON config: ../package.json
- TypeScript: ../tsconfig.json
- Plain text: ../LICENSE

### Code Files (should open in appropriate editor)
- JavaScript: ../out/extension.js (if exists after compilation)
- TypeScript: ../src/extension.ts
- Configuration: ../writerly.configuration.json

## Non-existent Files (These should show "File not found")

### Images
- missing-image.png
- ./assets/header.jpg
- "../images/logo.gif"

### Documents
- ./docs/manual.pdf
- "../guides/tutorial.md"
- `./config/settings.yaml`

## Edge Cases

### Paths with spaces
- "file with spaces.txt"
- '../folder with spaces/file.md'

### Paths with special characters
- file@name.txt
- file&name.json
- file%20encoded.html

### URLs (should not work - only local files supported)
- https://example.com/image.png
- http://localhost:3000/api/data.json
- ftp://server.com/file.txt

## Instructions

1. Place your cursor on any file path above
2. Press Cmd+Shift+O (Mac) or Ctrl+Shift+O (Windows/Linux)
3. Or use Command Palette: "Open File Under Cursor"
4. Hover over paths to see file information

## Expected Results

- ✅ Green paths should open successfully
- ❌ Red paths should show "File not found" message
- ℹ️ Blue paths should show hover information when available

Try different cursor positions within the same path to test the word detection logic.
